centralPacificOutlook.desc: 000<br />ACPN50 PHFO 261144<br />TWOCP <br /><br />Tropical Weather Outlook<br />NWS Central Pacific Hurricane Center Honolulu HI<br />200 AM HST Tue Nov 26 2024<br /><br />For the central North Pacific...between 140W and 180W:<br /><br />No tropical cyclones are expected during the next 7 days.<br /><br />The central North Pacific hurricane season officially ends on <br />November 30. The final Tropical Weather Outlook of the season will <br />be issued at 8 PM HST on November 30. Routine issuance of the <br />Tropical Weather Outlook will resume on June 1, 2025. During the <br />off-season, Special Tropical Weather Outlooks will be issued as <br />conditions warrant. <br /><br />$$<br /><br />Forecaster Gibbs
